Seanmag 888

Humanitarian, Medical Supplies and Equipment Supplier

Our Mission is to Make a Difference and Change Lives.

Discounts Applicable for Charities and Not-for-Profit Organizations

shop now

 

BUYING FOR YOUR HEALTHCARE CLINIC OR FACILITY?

 


IF YES, CLICK BELOW TO VISIT OUR CLINIC AND HOSPITAL SUPPLIES CATEGORY

click here

Providing Medical Supplies, Equipment and Humanitarian Aid Globally

Seanmag 888 is a Global Supplier for Healthcare Supplies and Equipment. We aim to offer our customers the best prices for medical supplies, medical devices, medical supplies, Vitamins and Supplements, hygienic supplies, water purification tablets, humanitarian products and more. Seanmag 888 is committed to ensuring our customers receive the right solutions to meet their needs through our extensive range to meet requested requirements. We will offer you great products from Australia and worldwide precured suppliers, great service and the best value every time. We believe in providing quality products which are tested prior to being committed to our inventory where we know our customers will be satisfied.
ABOUT OUR BRAND

Why you should choose Seanmag 888 to supply you!

 

Seanmag 888 strives to provide the best quality products where we are able to offer the lowest prices available in the Australian market, whether they are Seanmag 888 branded or procured from suppliers; who meet our high standards through our wide selection of products and brands. We will ensure that you receive genuine advice and offer the best products for your price range and desired use.

2021 PROGRESS

As of 2021, Seanmag 888 has added a SHOP where you can select and buy your selected quantity of product whenever you want carefree and easy for an amount you desire without having to purchase bulk amounts. We will offer you exceptional prices for small purchases with thousands of products to be added to our STORE in the coming months.

In addition, we will also be adding monthly and seasonal Coupons.

ABOUT US Register Now

Why Choose Seanmag 888?

Our branded products now and in the future are quality made, inexpensive, fast to deliver and easy to use in the most diverse environments throughout the world, whether it be with the use of water purification tablets, medical devices, hygienic products or our soon to be developed water purification systems. Our supplies of humanitarian medical products are tested for use prior to having the product being selected for our inventory.

What are the main key features
of our Aquarius brand?

Easy to use | Low Cost | Lightweight and transportable

CHARITIES AND NON-PROFIT
DISCOUNT

Seanmag 888 Offers Discounts to registered non-profit organizations and registered charities

Seanmag 888 provide a discount to registered non-profit organizations and registered charities. In both cases, we require the following information to determine your eligibility:

  1. Registered name of non-profit organization or charity
  2. Registered non-profit organization or charity number
    • For customers in Australia: ABN or CAN
    • For customers in in the continent of Africa: Business number/Registration for country registered.
    • For customers in UK: CRN
    • For customers in Canada:nine-digit BN/Registration number
    • For customers in U.S.:EIN number

 

As the discount can only be applied to the registered non-profit organization or charity, approved orders must be placed under our respective sales email and the company name listed as such. 

Please get in touch with our sales team at sales@saenmag888.com, where you will receive a fast response.

What we will do after your organization is approved for a discount.

Once your organization is approved for a discount, we will email you a quote for the item(s) you are ordering, and this will include the discount.

Please note that this offer is only valid towards regular priced products and cannot be used with another promotion, discount, or promo code. It will not be applicable to sale items.

 

 

Seanmag 888
Water Purification and medical accessory Wholesalers

Join our medical/humanitarian supply wholesalers, selling purchasing program and help people in need all over the world.

Seanmag 888 - Global Supply Chain Group

We have the solution! Fast and very effective bacterial disinfectant for the purification of water that contains viruses as well as effectively deactivating the chlorine-resistant pathogens Giardia and Cryptosporidium. We also offer single to individual purchases of medical accessories, Purchasing at bulk guarantees lower prices.

Contact us
